PrecisApproval of the re-appointment by the Minister of Transport of ROBERT MATTEAU, of Grand-Mère, Quebec, DONALD L. PETTIT, of West Vancouver, British Columbia, and MICHEL BIRON, of Nicolet, Quebec, as directors of the Board of Directors of VIA Rail Canada Inc. to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years.
